author: @aakibshaikh3864
text: 1. Learn concepts by applying them on real world problem. 2. Learn continuously(new and previous) and exponentially(increase your speed of learning and solving). 3. Start teaching data science. 4. Increase connection with data scientists of data science, ML, AI research and application. 5. Keep on exploring AI via google news, following industry leaders of research in ML, AI and data science on linkedin, twitter and other social media sites. 6. Keep learning from mistakes. 7. Keep reading and applying research papers of AI ( from my experience ).
